      "voiceId": "chris-williamson",
      "voiceName": "Chris Williamson",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "\u201cEverything is related to your genetics, both your smoking and your quitting smoking, both your addiction and your recovery. Even your belief in free will is heritable and is more similar in identical twins.\u201d \u2014 @kph3k\n\n\ud83d\udd17 open.spotify.com/episode/5jI\u2026",
