    {
      "voiceId": "chris-williamson",
      "voiceName": "Chris Williamson",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Reverse role models are everywhere.\n\n\u201cAs we pass through life, sometimes God shows us dopplegangers, bright or dark mirrors of ourselves, glimpses of how we might turn out if we zig or zag on the path ahead. Some of these people are meant as shining inspirations, others as terrible warnings, but they\u2019re all our teachers.\u201d \u2014 @slatestarcodex",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ChrisWillx/status/2033223861106577740",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-15T16:48:38+00:00",
